 Offsides -- Morocco: 5 (Chaouch 4, Hadji). Belgium: 3 (Weber 2, Degryse). 
</P>
<P>
 Saves -- Morocco: Azmi 12, Alaoui El Achraf 0. Belgium: Preud'homme 20. 
</P>
<P>
 Yellow Cards -- Morocco: Naybet (23rd minute), Daoudi (38th minute), Azzouzi 
(81st minute); Belgium, Grun (83rd minute), Weber (90th minute). 
</P>
<P>
 Red Cards -- None. 
</P>
<P>
 Referee -- Cadena, Colombia. Linesmen -- Calix Garcia, Honduras; Yli-Karro, 
Finland. 
</P>
<P>
 Attendance -- 60,790. LINEUPS 
</P>
