<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD CUP USA '94 / THE FIRST ROUND; FACTS AND FIGURES; SATURDAY'S LATE RESULT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 GROUP A 
</P>
<P>
 at Rose Bowl 
