<DOCID> 053134 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 20, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 5; National Desk 
</P>
