<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Five Acres: Actor Meschach Taylor's name was misspelled in a graphic on the 
Altadena-based program for troubled youth. 
</P>
